ow these consolations, taken together, reveal death as a blessing no matter how much we may love life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Feb 2020) 0aDeathxMoral and ethical aspects. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Death & Dying.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYUP eBook-Package 2016z978311066771440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300224702423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300224702.jpg  a978-3-11-066771-4  YUP eBook-Package 2016b2016  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aEBA_FAO